# Full-check after agentic changes

After making **any** code changes or completing plans/agent work, you **must** run `npm run full-check`.

- If it fails: fix the reported errors and run again until it passes.
- Exception: if failures are clearly in code you did not modify (pre-existing), complete the task and report those failures to the user instead of iterating.
- Do not consider the task done without full-check passing (or an explicit report of pre-existing failures).
